name: Pending SO for GST Migration
query:
SELECT 
	 so.name as "SO No:Link/Sales Order:80",
	 so.transaction_date as "Date:Date:80",
	 so.customer as "Customer:Link/Customer:80", 
	 sod.item_code as "ItemCode:Link/Item:80", 
	 sod.description as "Description::100",
	 sod.qty as "Ordered Qty:Float:50",
	 ifnull(sod.qty,0)-ifnull(sod.delivered_qty,0) as "Pend Qty:Float:50",
	 sod.base_net_rate as "Basic Rate:Currency:50", 
	 sod.base_rate as "Rate Inc:Currency:50", 
	 so.currency as "Cur:Link/Currency:50", 
	 so.selling_price_list as "Price List:Link/Price List:80", 
	 sod.name, so.taxes_and_charges, so.ignore_pricing_rule, so.track_trial

FROM
	 `tabSales Order` so, `tabSales Order Item` sod
WHERE
	 sod.parent = so.name
	 AND so.docstatus = 1
	 AND so.status != "Closed"
	 AND ifnull(sod.delivered_qty,0) < ifnull(sod.qty,0)
ORDER BY so.transaction_date desc
